        public void timeTick()
        Incremenet minutes by one. If minutes equals zero than increment hour. If s is true and hour is greater or equal to twelve than set hour to one. Else set ampmString to "AM". If ampmString equals AM than set ammpmString to "pm" else set it to "AM".
